cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper involves training neural agents to develop visual perception from raw image pixels and learn to communicate with a sequence of discrete symbols. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
